name: Tentacool
flavorText:
Drifts in shallow
seas. Anglers who
hook them by accident are
often punished by
its stinging acid.

previous.name: Victreebel
previous.flavorText:
Said to live in
huge colonies
deep in jungles, although no one
has ever returned
from there.

next.name: Tentacruel
next.flavorText:
The tentacles are
normally kept
short. On hunts, they are extended
to ensnare and
immobilize prey.
